  "operation_name": "aclnnApplyFusedEmaAdam",
  "description": "算子功能：实现FusedEmaAdam融合优化器功能。\n计算公式：\n$$(correction_{\\beta_1},correction_{\\beta_2},)=\\begin{cases}\n(1,1),&biasCorrection=False\\\\\n(1-\\beta_1^{step},1-\\beta_2^{step}),&biasCorrection=True\n\\end{cases}$$\n$$grad=\\begin{cases}\ngrad+weightDecay*var,&mode=0\\\\\ngrad,&mode=1\n\\end{cases}$$\n$$m_{out}=\\beta_1*m+(1-\\beta_1)*grad$$\n$$v_{out}=\\beta_2*v+(1-\\beta_2)*grad^2$$\n$$m_{next}=m_{out}/correction_{\\beta_1}$$\n$$v_{next}=v_{out}/correction_{\\beta_2}$$\n$$denom=\\sqrt{v_{next}}+eps$$\n$$update=\\begin{cases}\nm_{next}/denom,&mode=0\\\\\nm_{next}/denom+weightDecay*var,&mode=1\n\\end{cases}$$\n$$var_{out}=var-lr*update$$\n$$s_{out}=emaDecay*s+(1-emaDecay)*var_{out}$$",
  "api_flow": "two-step",
  "inter_parameter_constraints": [
    {
      "type": "shape_equality",
      "params": [
        "grad",
        "varRef",
        "mRef",
        "vRef",
        "sRef"
      ],
      "expr": "grad.shape == varRef.shape == mRef.shape == vRef.shape == sRef.shape",
      "description": "输入grad、varRef、mRef、vRef、sRef的shape必须保持一致。",
      "source": null,
      "target": null
    },
    {
      "type": "type_equality",
      "params": [
        "grad",
        "varRef",
        "mRef",
        "vRef",
        "sRef"
      ],
      "expr": "grad.dtype == varRef.dtype == mRef.dtype == vRef.dtype == sRef.dtype",
      "description": "输入grad、varRef、mRef、vRef、sRef的数据类型必须保持一致。",
      "source": null,
      "target": null
    }
  ],
